## What exactly is fixed

| Problem | Root cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| Overlay rotates with phone | `makeBillboard()` copied camera view matrix rotation | `SurfacePinner` extracts plane normal/right/up — rotation is 100% surface-relative |
| Overlay floating | Single hit-test, no depth refinement | `DepthPinner.estimateDepth()` averages 9 hit-tests across block area |
| Z-fighting flicker | Quad coplanar with ARCore plane mesh | 1mm z-offset toward camera in `DepthPinner.applyZOffset()` |
| Drift before lock | Anchor pose updates as ARCore learns | Translation-only updates pre-lock, rotation always fixed to plane |
| After lock still drifts | Anchors kept alive | `SurfacePinner.freeze()` detaches anchors, stores frozen matrix — nothing moves it |
| Size wrong at distance | Screen-pixel sizing | Real-world metres calculated from depth + FOV fraction |
| Blurry at distance | No mipmapping | `GL_LINEAR_MIPMAP_LINEAR` + `glGenerateMipmap` |